p: An. stephensi and An. gambaie larvae and pupae were exposed to different dilutions of the three hemp EOs obtained from the monoecious Felina 32 and female and male inflorescences of CS, and the mortality was recorded after 24 h of treatment. The doseâ€“response curves showed an insecticidal effect of the three EOs on larvae and pupae of An. stephensi ( Figure 2) and An. gambiae ( Figure 3). No effects were revealed when the mosquitoes were exposed to pure breeding in water or DMSO (control groups).
